data.description: This home would make a great primary residence or a rental property. It is a 3 bedroom 2 bath home and is a short walk to the beach as well as the City Park w/pickleball courts, tennis/basket ball courts, & a playground. Luxury vinyl plank throughout the house which is perfect for the beach life. The kitchen cabinets & countertops have been remodeled and their is a big cover patio for outdoor living! The master bedroom is big and accomodates a kind size bed. Big outdoor storge shed and nice size yard with fence and concrete driveway. New HVAC in 2021 roof in 2011. This home was a short term rental prior to the current owners and rented very well. Please do not park in the driveway it is in the process of being stained and sealed.
